<div class="badge badge-dark">PLATFORMS</div>
<h2 class="sec-h2">Marketplaces we work with</h2>
<div class="mp-grid">
<div class="mp-card">
<h3>Rozetka</h3>
<p>Ukraine's largest marketplace. Integration via Rozetka Seller API &mdash; orders arrive at the warehouse automatically. We pick, pack according to platform standards and ship via Nova Poshta or Rozetka courier. Labelling, barcoding and waybill printing &mdash; all included.</p>
</div>
<div class="mp-card">
<h3>Prom.ua</h3>
<p>Over 200,000 sellers on the platform. Through Prom API integration, orders reach our WMS in seconds. Automatic waybill generation, real-time inventory sync, status updates &mdash; you simply monitor sales in your dashboard.</p>
</div>
<div class="mp-card">
<h3>Kasta</h3>
<p>Fashion marketplace with strict packaging and delivery requirements. MTP Group ensures full compliance with Kasta standards: branded bags, proper labelling, same-day shipping. API integration &mdash; inventory and orders sync automatically.</p>
</div>
<div class="mp-card">
<h3>OLX Delivery</h3>
<p>For OLX sellers using the "OLX Delivery" option. We store your goods, and when a buyer places an order &mdash; we quickly pick and ship. We handle all product types: electronics, clothing, accessories, home goods.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div></section>

<!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
<section class="how-it-works"><div class="ctr">
<div class="badge">HOW IT WORKS</div>
