<div class="step-card"><div class="step-num">03</div><h3>Shipping</h3><p>The waybill is generated automatically. The parcel is handed to the carrier &mdash; Nova Poshta, Meest, Justin or courier delivery. The status updates on the marketplace automatically.</p></div>
<div class="step-card"><div class="step-num">04</div><h3>Monitoring and reports</h3><p>You track everything through your dashboard: inventory, order statuses, returns, financial reports. Full transparency without a single call to the warehouse.</p></div>
</div>
</div></section>

