<div class="badge">FAQ</div>
<h2 class="sec-h2">Frequently asked questions</h2>
<div class="faq-list">
<div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q">How much does marketplace fulfillment cost?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>Shipping &mdash; from 18 UAH per order at 200+ shipments/day. Storage &mdash; from 650 UAH per m&sup3;/mo. Minimum fee &mdash; 5,000 UAH/mo. The higher the volume &mdash; the lower the per-unit price.</p></div></div>
<div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q">Which marketplaces do you integrate with?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>Rozetka, Prom.ua, Kasta, OLX. We also work with CRM systems: KeyCRM, SalesDrive, Horoshop. Any platform with an API &mdash; integration in 2-4 hours.</p></div></div>
<div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q">How quickly can we get started?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>Onboarding takes 1-3 days. Day 1: consultation, contract, marketplace integration. Day 2: goods transfer, WMS scanning. Day 3: test shipments and launch. Most clients start shipping on day 2.</p></div></div>
<div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q">Can I sell on multiple platforms at once?</button><div class="faq-a"><p>Yes, and that is one of the key advantages. A single warehouse, a single inventory &mdash; while orders from all marketplaces are processed in one place. Inventory syncs in real time, eliminating overselling.</p></div></div>
